// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0727 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a3806dc4-b6ab-5ae1-be61-61afed507312

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
